Class Rooms

  • java.lang.Object
    • Rooms
  • public class Rooms
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is part of the Lockdown application. Lockdown is a very simple, text based adventure game. An object of class Rooms stores a list of rooms. It is used to get random rooms for the people of the game.
